text:
🐦Hillock Park is a little park linked by a beautifully landscaped land bridge over a road below to the Bidadari Park.
🦜The Hillock Park provided a green sanctuary for migratory birds, as well as for residents of Woodleigh Glen.
🐦‍⬛The Hillock Park green sanctuary was deliberately left without any footpath or lighting to preserve its natural habitat.
🐧It's a serene little Park for a relaxing stroll or walk the dog.
Connected to Bidadari park by a big bridge. Very interesting to extend your walk after Bidadari park.
